OL,3,CHouseholds to start receiving #299
OL,4,Ccost-of-living payments
OL,6,FHouseholds on low incomes will start
OL,7,Fgetting a #299 cost-of-living payment
OL,8,Ffrom Tuesday.
OL,10,FPayments will be made across the UK by
OL,11,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions
OL,12,F(DWP) between February 6 and 22.
OL,14,FIt is the third of up to three
OL,15,Fpayments over 2023/24, totalling up to
OL,16,F#900, which are being paid to eligible
OL,17,Fhouseholds on means-tested benefits.
OL,19,FThey come as part of a support package
OL,20,Fwhich has been helping households
OL,21,Fsince autumn 2021.
