OL,3,CHouseholds to start receiving #299
OL,4,Ccost-of-living payments
OL,6,FThose receiving tax credits only will
OL,7,Freceive payments from HM Revenue and
OL,8,FCustoms (HMRC) between February 16 and
OL,9,F22.
OL,11,FThe payments will be sent out
OL,12,Fautomatically and recipients do not
OL,13,Fneed to apply to receive them.
OL,15,FMel Stride, Secretary of State for
OL,16,FWork and Pensions, said: "The economy
OL,17,Fhas turned a corner, and with
OL,18,Finflation falling we are providing
OL,19,Fmillions of the most vulnerable
OL,20,Fhouseholds with another significant
OL,21,Fcash boost."
