OL,6,FUK government minister for Scotland
OL,7,FJohn Lamont said: "This crucial cost-
OL,8,Fof-living payment will benefit more
OL,9,Fthan 680,000 people across Scotland."
OL,11,FWelsh Secretary David TC Davies said:
OL,12,F"Over 400,000 households in Wales will
OL,13,Fbe receiving this payment directly
OL,14,Finto their bank accounts to help them
OL,15,Fwith the cost of living."
OL,17,FThe UK government said it will
OL,18,Fcontinue to support vulnerable people
OL,19,Fwith the cost of living from April by
OL,20,Fuprating benefits in line with
OL,21,Finflation by 6.7%.
