OL,6,FIt will also maintain the triple lock,
OL,7,Fwhich protects pensions value from
OL,8,Finflation, and increase the state
OL,9,Fpension by 8.5%, among other measures.
OL,11,FAccording to figures released by the
OL,12,FInsolvency Service last week, the
OL,13,Fnumber of people needing breathing
OL,14,Fspace from their debts jumped by 25%
OL,15,Fin 2023, compared with the previous
OL,16,Fyear.
