OL,6,FThis is a scheme which gives someone
OL,7,Fin debt protection from their
OL,8,Fcreditors - meaning they must stop
OL,9,Flegal action against a person while
OL,10,Fthe breathing space is in place.
OL,12,FAcross England and Wales, there were
OL,13,F88,390 registered breathing spaces in
OL,14,F2023, comprised of 86,928 standard and
OL,15,F1,462 mental health breathing space
OL,16,Fregistrations, the Insolvency Service
OL,17,Fsaid.
