OL,6,FA standard breathing space is
OL,7,Favailable to people with problem debt
OL,8,Fand gives legal protections from
OL,9,Fcreditor action for up to 60 days.
OL,11,FA mental health crisis breathing space
OL,12,Fis available to someone who is
OL,13,Freceiving mental health crisis
OL,14,Ftreatment. It lasts as long as the
OL,15,Fperson's mental health crisis
OL,16,Ftreatment, plus 30 days.
